{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"757f837e86","title":"念奴娇·鸟儿问答","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e45fe29267","index":0,"year":1965,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"757f837e86"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"114a6bd538","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"鹏，这里指大鱼变成的大鸟，作衰义用。"},{"id":"f665bc8be1","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"九万里，翻动扶摇羊角，《庄子·逍遥游》：“鹏之徒于南宾也，水击三千里，转扶摇而上者九万里。”“有鸟最，其名为鹏，背若泰山，翼若垂天之云，转扶摇羊角而上者九万里，绝云气，负青天，然后图南，且适（往）南宾也。意思都是说大鹏在向南海飞的时候，凭着旋风的力量，翻动翅膀，飞上九万里高空。扶摇和羊角都是旋风的名称。"},{"id":"3638a0b6fb","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"蓬间雀，即《庄子·逍遥游》中的“斤鸡”。"},{"id":"250745e4b5","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"琼阁，琼楼玉宇，仙人住处。"},{"id":"a4a2e17b97","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"订了三家条约，指苏、美、英三国1963年8月5日在莫斯科签订的《禁止在大气层、外层空间和水下进行核武器试验条约》。"},{"id":"6fad2adf40","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"土豆烧熟了，再加牛肉，苏联领导人赫鲁晓夫1964年4月曾在一次演说中说“福利共产主义”是“一盘土豆烧牛肉的好菜”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6056adfd70","type":"title","text":"念奴娇·鸟儿问答","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"},{"id":"114a6bd538","type":"paragraph","text":"鲲鹏展翅，九万里，翻动扶摇羊角。l）背负青天朝下看，都是人间城郭。炮火连天，弹痕遍地，吓倒蓬间雀。怎么得了，哎呀我要飞跃。借问君去何方，雀儿答道：有仙山琼阁\"不见前年秋月朗，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"},{"id":"f665bc8be1","type":"subtitle","text":"订了三家条约。以","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"},{"id":"3638a0b6fb","type":"paragraph","text":"还有吃的，土豆烧熟了，","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"},{"id":"250745e4b5","type":"subtitle","text":"再加牛肉。以","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"},{"id":"a4a2e17b97","type":"paragraph","text":"不须放屁，试看天地翻覆。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86"}],"page":{"id":"77c0d8bf64","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"757f837e86","start":204,"end":205}}}},"__N_SSG":true}